            <td colspan="2" class="titulo2" valign="top"><strong><em>Interlitq’s</em> “The Groves of Academe” series: </strong><br><br>

<strong>Interview with <a href="http://www.interlitq.org/issue20/allen-hibbard/bio.php">Dr. Allen Hibbard</a>,<br><bR>
Professor of English, Middle Tennessee State University,<br><br>
